reviews.review_text: Intriguing AUD I comment here only on the sound quality. First impression is an overall muffled quality, but in fact the bass is really punchy and carries everything along. Sounds almost like the mic was hidden down below head level with no direct shot at the PA. There are stereo problems with dropouts in one channel. Lot's of warts, but it does give a solid impression of what they must have sounded like on the night, and you can feel the groove. And the Scarlet is rockin!
